TBS CHAMPIONSHIP: MERCEDES MONE DEF. HIKARU SHIDA

Pretty damn good match that ends when Kamille gives Shida a Big Booty behind the ref's back and allows Mercedes to his the Mone Maker.

Post match, Britt Baker's music hits. Kamille attacks a random fan for rocking a Sting mask the way Britt did a few weeks ago. But it was not her

Britt attacks Mercedes from behind and takes the TBS CHAMPIONSHIP to hold in the sky

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0fbefa63-1344-4022-9d80-e08725b03b55/20240814_172248.jpg?format=original)

